{
  "texts": [
    "These scientific contributions are better discussed along this paper.",
    "Table 2 summarizes the answers to the input research questions.",
    "The second column (Longitudinal inputs) indicates the vocabulary (lexicon) used in each approach (InpRQ1).",
    "Many papers (Li et al. 2020; Rao et al. 2022a, Florez et al. 2021, Pang et al. 2021, Prakash et al. 2021) use standardized categorical codes of diagnosis (e.g., ICD), medications, and other health elements as part of their vocabulary.",
    "Some papers mix categorical and continuous data (Li et al. 2023a, b; Rao et al. 2022b)."
  ]
}